  PreLevelDialogue:
  - Kid, that cutting, it brought a tear to my ear. It really did. I think you are
    nearly ready for the big leagues kid!
  - Key word being nearly.
  - "I\u2019ve got a final test for you. This will determine if you are truly fit
    to be a SAMURAI SCULPTOR!"
  - "A commercial one at that, one that is going to sculpt our bank accounts into
    being 100 times RICHER! I\u2019m getting giddy just thinking about it!"
  - "Alright alright, no more dreaming, I\u2019ve got the marble, I\u2019ve got your
    last training target, and you\u2019ve got your sword!"
  - Do we have an understanding? GREAT!
